            "description": "For the smaller projects I am a Project Leader or Project Manager. These projects often start as a request to solve a problem. The solutions vary from installing a new (line of ) machine(s), small adaptations in an existing system or replacing a complete system. I am responsible for planning, budget, quality and other resources required for the project. The internal Project team can consist of members from the production, purchasing maintenance, process, E&I and sometimes research departments. For the bigger or more complex projects external engineering support for the internal project team can be hired. This can lead to an engineering contractor cooperation or only hiring external individual support. In case of a EC, I act as a project manager for the external project leader of the EC.",
